LOCUS       UEA_013_(7SK-white-eye) 8617 bp ds-DNA     circular     07-MAY-2025
DEFINITION  .
COMMENT     UEA_013 (7SK-white-eye) is a plasmid that uses the same sequence as
            UEA_012 (white-eye gRNA HDR) however has a swapped out Pol3
            promoeter from U6.1 to the putative promoeter 7SK.  Sequencing:
            Plasmidsaurus Nanopore sequenced post midiprep and MC ultrafree
            column purification, see notes in Lab Notes - 7SK Novel Pol III
            Promoter Plasmid Assembly in April 2025.  Notes On Plasmid:
            In-Silico design: In-Silico 7SK-white-eye Plasmid Design  Plasmid
            designing and assembly: Lab Notes - 7SK Novel Pol III Promoter
            Plasmid Assembly
